    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. CFD predictions of hemolysis index fall within 12% of experimental measurements across all 5 operating points. The relative hemolysis index RH satisfies the acceptance criterion RH < 1 for the identified worst-case operating condition (6 L/min, 3500 RPM). The model is credible for its intended use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
